Reasoning: The paper deals with algorithmic problems on graphs, specifically the Subset Feedback Vertex Set problem and its variants, on graphs of bounded independent set size. This makes it relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Graph Theory (cs.GT), and Computational Complexity (cs.CC).
